coming to visit you in New York and only had

00:29:11.453 --> 00:29:12.453
time for one meal, where would you take him
or her and what dish would you get?

00:29:12.453 --> 00:29:13.453
&gt;&gt;Frank: I, I can't answer that because I,
I'd ask the friend a bunch of questions, you

00:29:13.453 --> 00:29:18.429
know what I mean? Like, one meal I, I, is
just, is the friend in the mood for Italian?

00:29:18.429 --> 00:29:22.370
Does the friend, if the friends coming from
Italy, I'm not gonna take him or her to an

00:29:22.370 --> 00:29:27.470
Italian restaurant. Does the friend want a
semi-formal experience? Does the friend want,

00:29:27.470 --> 00:29:32.759
what is currently the most chattered about
thing? For a while there like, the kind of

00:29:32.759 --> 00:29:36.890
split the difference place you never, that
you never kind of bombed out if you took someone

00:29:36.890 --> 00:29:41.820
to was Momofuku Ssam Bar because it was very
