00:48:09.799 --> 00:48:11.650
&gt;&gt;Frank: Sure.

00:48:11.650 --> 00:48:25.630
&gt;&gt;female audience member #10: Hi. I was wondering
what was the reason for the change of your

00:48:25.630 --> 00:48:26.630
subtitle for your book from the hardcover
to the soft cover? And also, I was wondering,

00:48:26.630 --> 00:48:27.630
in your book you talk about your relationship
with food and how portion control was the

00:48:27.630 --> 00:48:28.630
most important thing. And I was just wondering,
psychologically, what was the most important

00:48:28.630 --> 00:48:29.630
part about getting the, kind of keeping the--

00:48:29.630 --> 00:48:31.279
&gt;&gt;Frank: Ok. The subtitle changed for two
reasons. One was, the previous subtitle was

00:48:31.279 --> 00:48:36.990
"The Secret History of a Full Time Eater,"
I think that's right, the full time eater

00:48:36.990 --> 00:48:43.500
reference was a double entendre, it, it, it
