00:49:09.670 --> 00:49:13.310
on family stories and on the kind of family
members whose portraits I painted in the book

00:49:13.310 --> 00:49:18.349
as their favorite part of it. And so we thought
why not just adjust the subtitle so it's clear

00:49:18.349 --> 00:49:25.180
that this isn't, this isn't just or even primarily
inside tales of a restaurant critic book,

00:49:25.180 --> 00:49:30.140
but it's really a, a full-bodied family memoir.
And so, I don't know, I don't know if you've

00:49:30.140 --> 00:49:31.671
looked at it or read it, but I mean--

00:49:31.671 --> 00:49:34.079
&gt;&gt;audience member #10: I read the hardcover.
